data.description: Charming two story residence located in the heart of Missoula. This picturesque 4 bedroom, 3 bath, 2 lot property boasts the surrounding setting and landscape with mature trees, pond, & seasonal lush gardens.  With a plus size 14x26 sqft greenhouse & landscape/compost area, you can continue providing a unique space of relaxation and scenery every change of season.  A large kitchen, with extended island can provide enough to handle large groups of friends and neighbors.   Schedule a showing today and prepare to fall in love with your new hidden gem haven. By appointment only. Contact Tom Frister at 406-370-9268 or your real estate professional for any questions. Owner was previously approved for PTAP program with MT Dept Revenue. Contact MT Dept of Revenue for current 2023 tax assessment and billing. No Lock box.
